for (const sig of ['SIGTERM', 'SIGINT']) {
  process.on(sig, () => server.close(() => process.exit(0)));
}
```

## 7. CORS is undefined
Default Express has no CORS. Decide explicitly — either no cross-origin access, or an allowlist via the `cors` package. Don't enable `*` blindly if credentials will ever be sent.

## 8. Logging
`console.log` isn't structured and logs nothing about requests. Use `pino` or `morgan` with a redaction list so tokens/emails aren't written to logs.

