### 3. Missing security middleware
- No [`helmet`](https://helmetjs.github.io/) — so no `X-Content-Type-Options`, `Strict-Transport-Security`, CSP, etc.
- No CORS policy (`cors` middleware with an explicit allowlist).
- No rate limiting (`express-rate-limit`) — endpoints are wide open to brute force/scraping.
