Unhandled errors in Express fall through to the default handler, which leaks stack traces in dev mode and may hang requests. Add an error-handling middleware as the **last** `app.use(...)`:

```js
app.use((err, req, res, next) => {
  console.error(err);                       // log full detail server-side
  const status = err.status || 500;
  res.status(status).json({
