1. Add error-handling + 404 middleware and `server.on('error')`. *(correctness)*
2. Add `helmet`, disable `x-powered-by`, set JSON body size limits. *(security, quick win)*
3. Add rate limiting. *(security)*
4. Introduce schema validation (`zod`/`joi`) now, before more routes are added. *(security)*
5. Gate `/users` behind auth or strip emails. *(data exposure)*
6. Graceful shutdown + `PORT` from env. *(ops)*
7. Swap `console.log` for a structured logger. *(ops/security)*

