| **P1** | Input validation (zod/joi), rate limiting, auth on `/users`, structured logging |
| **P2** | Graceful shutdown, env-based config, CORS whitelist, process-level error handlers |
| **P3** | Health-check minimization, tests for error paths, dependency scanning |

