| Body size | `app.use(express.json({ limit: '10kb' }));` |
| PII in responses | `/users` returns emails unauthenticated — require auth or omit the email field. |
| Trust proxy | If behind a load balancer, `app.set('trust proxy', 1);` so `req.ip` is correct for rate limiting. |
